reviewText: A great movie. Moving, inspirational, dramatic, heartfelt, genuine, honest, etc, etc. A great story and great film-making.  If you get the chance, see it!!
Yes - I WOULD GIVE SIX STARS IF IT WERE POSSIBLE!!... I saw it while in Brazil, it is a shame we can't get it in the US. SO INSPIRATIONAL SO BEAUTIFUL! A Hymn to the human spirit.
